('35598812', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Keeps changing playlists, very annoying.', 'I used to love Spotify (I use the free version) and their playlists. I play one for my daughter at bedtime, but I now have to stop using Spotify because the playlist would change to another one in the middle of her music. NOT appropriate rock music for bedtime. I cannot even control which playlist it goes to nor why it does this. This is a really poor functioning of this app when you\'re using it for a child. I don\'t mind the ads, but to then change it to some rap or techno in the middle does not make me a fan. \n\nI\'ve checked online about this issue and none of the fixes work and there are many people who are having this issue. Until they fix this, I won\'t be using Spotify for my child. Very unfortunate.', '198447746', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Very good', 'Excellent Of the best', 'Spotify', 0.127072, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'all', 156, -1, 2, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
