('15737676', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Worthless', 'Yes very harsh title you\'ll see why I think this driving gps app needs to be retired or the algorithms need to be rewritten. Oh wait, better yet, use AI instead. Or a robot. Or a self driving car. The hyper loop. You get my point.  All this tech is great but needs A LOT of work.  The app doesn\'t do what it\'s supposed to do. I live in two of the worse traffic areas LA and the Bay Area. My commute is 40 miles each way can take 30 mins or 3 hrs. The rub is lately Waze thinks it\'s saving (a whole 2 mins) me time by changing my route (exiting freeway and driving on residual roads) when in actuality adds more commute time. The delay message pops up and up and up. Example, the route Waze suggested would get me home in hour 15. I followed the suggested route and I waited for 45 mins to get on a freeway. The entrance was 1000 feet away. Tons and tons of traffic. The app isn\'t improving driving it\'s making it worse. \n\nEveryone on the planet is using Waze and sending everyone on the same route. Defeats the propose of the app. It\'s become so mainstream and tons of users. The backend can\'t handle or manage the information the drivers are generating to recalculate a better route for others to follow. \n\nI know it\'s not Waze fault for the traffic. Traffic is part of driving in California. \n\nI the app is worthless for me to use. I\'ll stick to driving the crazy freeways of Northern and Southern California. If it\'s to nasty I\'ll find a nice bar to relax. BTW, I have deleted the app.', '162628718', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Great application!', 'Excellent application! Updated maps and very good help to avoid traffic and reach unknown places.', 'Waze', 0.0763016, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 380, 0, 3, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
('158729226', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Location services- always', 'I love wade however I have having to keep location on all the time. It kills my battery and makes me look for am alternative. They should really consider having an option for using location services only when using the app.', '100849232', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Poor choice of route', 'I have noticed that it does not consider the best route, if route options are requested is even worse, why to keep the initial as the best, the optional routes it proposes are crazy. You should have the option of having the user propose a route to compare.', 'Waze', 0.20325, 0, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 381, 2, -1, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
('162869145', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great App!', 'Uses a lot of my battery but is really great!', '227506382', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Great app', 'It is a great navigation tool, a lot of help !!', 'Waze', 0.471198, 2, 3, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 382, 4, 3, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('16297951', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Fun but needs few things', 'V4.16\nWow what happened!? Almost everything broken since this last update. Choose 3D it shows 2d, while navigating it keeps moving the map to your destination and telling you that you arrived like every 10-40 seconds. Omg like everything is broken. And how many times must I request night mode needs to be night mode on all screens. No use having night mode then getting blinded when you need to go to a menu\nSo this last update brought tons of bugs. You went from 5 to 4 to now a 1 star until these are fixed. \n\n----\nQuick update to last review.  Tried the GPS really like it over all other GPS. Few problems with it. It\'s a little wordy and need ability to turn off most of the voices. It shouldn\'t tell you to turn THREE TIMES within 1/4 mile!  Worst part It talks over you when you are using the phone! Annoying and must be fixed! Needs low tones just like built in nav when using phone. \n\n3.7.2 New version update\n\nSomething things fixed which is nice. Things I think need to be fixed:\n\n• Notification must work when minimized\n \n• Pop-up messages should be dark in night mode\n \n• Pop up messages need to be layered with the newest in back of others \n \n• On road notices need to be the same as on the shoulder (example stalled car in a lane not on side of road)\n \n• Popular items need less clicks - vehicle, police, accident\n \n• Traffic needs to be more automated\n \n• Fire hazards need to be added - vehicle fire, fire on side of road, fire vehicles etc\n\nNeed to offer cng and biodiesel fuels\n\nBtw I have knight status and use quite often but like others said I don\'t use the GPS/navigation function as its pretty bad. Only tried a few times and takes way to many clicks to find anything. Ill try it more and see if I can review better\n\n------\nUsing a few weeks now.  Need faster 1-2 click to report more common things.  Car on shoulder , accident, police. Etc. also need car on road not just shoulder. Anything that is done while driving needs to be simplified. Too many clicks. Also need ability to click anywhere to send a report- does not feature that. Also should be able to tag while on the phone (with Verizon can\'t) and put in info after data connection back. Also what gives. I\'m always told I\'m reporting too much. Well there are always lots of things to report. Just raise that maximum a little.  I might report two cars, one police, traffic and debris all in 1 mile\n\n---', '139435173', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Very good', 'It is very good app, in fact I prefer to use it before google maps, although it would be well to optimize the battery consumption since you get off fast and as for the maps, perhaps it is more convenient to have more street names in order to be able to visualize them better, or Put more points of reference of establishments so that it works better the search of places in the map.', 'Waze', 0.229083, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 383, -1, 2, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
('165916904', 'applestore', 'United States', 'What happened to the sound?!', 'I used to love using Waze, but they recently \"fixed\" something with the sound. Now I can\'t hear anything but a mumble when I\'m in the app. I can only hear it when I click out of the app, so then I can\'t see the map to make sure I\'m turning on the correct street.\nIt\'s also begun to not say the street name. Just \"turn right in 500 feet.\" Its also been very delayed if it does tell me to turn. It\'s very frustrating and has caused me to miss my turn on more than several occasions. \nThis app used to be great and easy to use. Now it\'s causing my drive to be way more stressful.\nPlans to fix these soon?', '391578103', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Wonderful', 'A safe way to make the transfers. And more with so much speed restrictions on different roads. Correct it in the option to be able to locate a locality and from there add it to the favorites. But the route confuses her and sends you in another direction. Overall excellent and very reliable', 'Waze', 0.247729, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 384, -1, 2, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
('166603829', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Mostly reliable & easy to use', 'Many times this app has saved me valuable time and is easy to use! My biggest complaints are I can\'t tell the difference between quirky supposed \"short cuts\" and real trouble ahead, and like all apps for travel time they tend to underestimate the time for traffic lights and thus sometimes take you on alternate routes that at best are no better that staying on the high way and just gritting your teeth.', '351440788', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Good application', 'I have been using the application for several years, and I have noticed that there are update versions that are unstable, like the current one, does not give the best routes and the approximate time of arrival has a high margin of error', 'Waze', 0.20441, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 385, 1, 0, 0.875, 'ot', 'br'),
