('177327066', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Different from the PC version', 'I use Spotify on my computer all the time. In this format, I\'m able to listen to whichever tracks I want, and in the order I arranged them. It\'s one of the reasons I love this player over others. However, in the app, it\'s almost like a knock off of Pandora; everything is on shuffle, and the \"suggested tracks\" have nothing to do with my playlist style. What\'s worse, when I click \"click this video for 30 minutes of ad-free music,\" the app crashes and plays about 3 more commercials in a row. This bug still needs to be fixed, even after the new update.', '494529520', 'applestore', 'Mexico', '?', 'It is very good but it could improve in the sense that there is no premium and one free with not all the functions, also that in the free version there are unlimited jumps to the next song, if they do that I will put the 5 stars?', 'Spotify', 0.225401, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 389, 0, 2, 0.75, 'br', 'ot'),
