('179482004', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Awesome app!', 'Still only three stars. Really sick and tired of the stupid ads that pop up when the car is stopped. This is the time I take a longer peak at the directions. But half the screen is now taken up with a soulless, evil MacDonnalds ad!!! Sure, I could tap below the screen to make it go away. But I try not to fidget with the phone while driving, including when temporarily stopped. I would gladly pay a reasonable fee for ad free, pretty sure others would too.', '4843', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Excellent app', 'Very good and very useful. Widely recommended', 'Waze', 0.0116184, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 391, 0, 3, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
