('186855874', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Constant GPS access even when app is not in use', 'The GPS function never shuts off. It ALWAYS stays on, even after closing the app. Yes, I said \"close\" as in actually closed and not running in the background. It drains battery so ridiculously quick that I have to disable GPS for the app when I don\'t use it, which makes loading it up really annoying because I have to re-enable GPS access while I\'m using it. If the app is closed there is NO reason for it to be accessing GPS data in the background.', '43926880', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'The best app!', 'Simply the best GPS application', 'Waze', 0.208597, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 396, -3, 2, 0.375, 'ot', 'ot'),
