('220101252', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Very BAD update - can\'t even control playlists', 'I agree with several reviewers - this last update was a BAD one. The app now plays random songs instead of the ones in the selected playlist. My daughter goes from listening to Sofia the First to some random international music. \n\nI used to use Spotify to make a lot of playlists. Looks like I\'ll have to switch to another player.', '42010641', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Excellent', 'The best way to listen to music, when you do not have Pandora', 'Spotify', 0.140602, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 415, -1, 3, 0.5, 'ot', 'ot'),
