('23363265', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Good App but huge power drain on phones', 'Great app but it needs to have the option to be on only when app is being used instead of just the always or never options in the location services controls on the iPhone. The biggest complaint I hear from people who use the app is it\'s a huge power hog tracking location all the time. Drains the phones in no time.', '265708898', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Very good app to avoid traffic', 'The only thing I put it on but is that some data are wrong in the directions sometimes the good thing is that it is not very frequent', 'Waze', 0.211228, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 417, 0, 1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('236924082', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Becoming unreliable', 'The app is becoming more and more unreliable. It randomly drops the Bluetooth even when the Bluetooth is working for phone calls.  It used to be when that happened it would default to the speaker but now it is sometimes defaulting to the phone and more often making no sound at all. It\'s unpredictability is making me concerned whether it\'s safe to use app since I need to look at screen to determine whether it is working.', '4843', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Excellent app', 'Very good and very useful. Widely recommended', 'Waze', 0.0229495, 0, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 418, 0, 3, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
