('39577181', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Used to be Awesome...', 'Absolutely loved this app in the beginning; however, it has steadily gone down hill. On top of eating up battery life like crazy, it tends to have you exit off the highway just to get back on. It changes your route and doesn\'t notify you until it\'s suddenly telling you to exit. They\'ve also sold out and you now have pop up adds that take up half the screen or more. If you accidentally touch it (when trying to get rid of it) it opens your browser and can mean a few extra u-turns at times. Just go back to how it was before the sell out and it will be great again.', '242303175', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'I did not arrive without Waze', 'I can not go out or come back without Waze. My suggestion to improve the application is to identify and ask if you agree that it will take you to the streets with some risk to make time. Or go for safer roads', 'Waze', 0.222729, 1, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 528, 3, 1, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
