('541839721', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Great app, you guys just gotta work out some things', 'I love this app, especially for exercising, but there are some things that you guys need to reconsider. For one, it\'s Spotify premium, it is just way too much money, 12 dollars a month, that is just too much for music on the run. I know that there are special offers that offer 3 dollars a month for 3 months, but that should be your normal price every month, your ads alone should give you adequate upkeep. Also the mobile version should be like the PC and iPad versions, unlimited skips and you can actually choose which songs you would like to listen to, the limited skips and forcing people to shuffle play is just a trick to make you buy premium, though I know it is one of those scenarios with \"it\'s not personal, it\'s just business\", that is a bit much don\'t you think? Also the ads are okay, but 3 in a row, each 30 seconds long, that just ruins the moment for the person trying to listen to his/her music, but you have my approval to keep that feature if you fix everything else. Though I still really like this app, it is better than most other music apps, keep it up!', '203199967', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Excellent!', 'I always use it, it is rare not to find the music you are looking for', 'Spotify', 0.220725, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 656, 2, 4, 0.75, 'ot', 'ot'),
