('542237550', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Limited', 'Don\'t get me wrong, I love Spotify. But since I got a phone, (or maybe it\'s the recent update) Spotify isn\'t how it was. I have the free version and I can\'t choose certain songs to listen to, even when I play playlists random songs not in the playlist will play, and I can\'t repeat songs. All of which I can do on my iPad (older version) and my computer. This is really annoying because, when I have a playlist of clean, FOB, songs a random FOB song will play that\'s not even in the playlist! Please make the free version on iPhones less limited!', '101362156', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'I loved', 'The best App to listen to your music, your playlist. The best is the premium version', 'Spotify', 0.227632, 1, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 658, -2, 3, 0.375, 'br', 'ot'),
