('6160734', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Need to change the location services', 'The app either allows you to be tracked always or never. They\'ve removed the option of \"while using the app\".  I love the app but won\'t be using it until this is changed. Other apps that have tried this have met with stiff customer resistance and hope the same will happen here.', '209548916', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Bad with the addresses ...', 'Including an address is a headache! The address of my house is not correct! It sends you to the number or location of the street that has the registered App! I\'ve lost Waze more than five times !!!! I use to check the traffic level but in terms of location and speed, I am disappointed! Always look for the longest way !!!! Evil!!!!', 'Waze', 0.201957, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 668, 2, -2, 0.5, 'ot', 'ot'),
