('86778577', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Waze', 'Great great great app. Use it all the time', '409231224', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Great great', 'Very good app is great !!', 'Waze', 0.724153, 4, 2, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 671, 3, 4, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('86792951', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Pretty good, but...', 'Not a hard core user but find it pretty good. I generally use it concurrently with my native iOS maps (which handles the turn by turn work). Waze provides the audio alerts for police, hazards and so on. One major irritation: Waze audio come in about twice the volume of maps. Also irritating are the start up screens that are a serious pain when driving and trying to clear the stupid screen to get to the main display... Marking the location of police activity is simple and straightforward... The use of the other icons are not so intuitiv, though I\'ve never really bothered to figure them out. When making a long trip I found the limitation of a max trip of 1,000 miles also irritating (hence the dual use of maps to nav and Waze to alert.', '139435173', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Very good', 'It is very good app, in fact I prefer to use it before google maps, although it would be well to optimize the battery consumption since you get off fast and as for the maps, perhaps it is more convenient to have more street names in order to be able to visualize them better, or Put more points of reference of establishments so that it works better the search of places in the map.', 'Waze', 0.223537, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 672, -1, 2, 0.625, 'ot', 'ot'),
('87402323', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Is good!', 'Works really good the only thing that could change is the location services is always on it should be a option to be while  using that\'s the only thing I hope they wok on that', '49268868', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'GPS while the app is in use', 'The app is very good, but I should use GPS only when the app is enuso, not all the time', 'Waze', 0.290581, 4, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 673, 2, 2, 1, 'ot', 'ot'),
('87790719', 'applestore', 'United States', 'I like it, but it needs improvement', 'I like all the features except the fact that it does not give you alternate routes with ETA like google map does.  Still prefer Google Maps', '417107738', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Excellent service', 'The service is 1st in 99 of every 100 times. I always get out of trouble and suggest the best way. Only once did not have the address identified, but except on that occasion the rest of the time has worked great', 'Waze', 0.103835, 1, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 674, 1, 2, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('9140417', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Most excellent traffic navigator', 'D.C. NOVA traffic stupid. One day on the way home the beltway was shut down about 5 miles ahead of me. App showed me how to get home through back roads in 30 mins vs 3 hours. Impossible to give app enough praise', '165490771', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'Heated iphone 6', 'It heated the phone a lot and the battery consumed it very fast this happened after an update x that uninstall it', 'Waze', 0.0130404, 0, 0, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 675, 2, 1, 0.875, 'ot', 'ot'),
('9579898', 'applestore', 'United States', 'Best navigator/co-driver I\'ve had for a long time', 'Waze works cause we all believe in it and we use it... And the more of us who join, the better it will work... See you on the highways...\nThe best ...  cause it really works.', '348568716', 'applestore', 'Mexico', 'The best', 'The best app to travel ??', 'Waze', 0.21059, 3, 1, 0, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'long', 676, 1, 1, 1, 'ot', 'ot');
